{"tid":2157071,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"成隊巴塞都要重建","createTime":"2020-08-14T21:03:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T22:53:34.000Z","uid":158841,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5dd471c0f5ac62b79665e14eca5606855997c3c8","tid":2157071,"uid":158841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T21:03:09.000Z","msg":"本身自己無話特別支持邊隊 睇完埋波覺得幾爽 好多入波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成隊巴塞跑得慢 唔願跑 無鬥心 條防線好似紙牌咁 美斯隱形 成隊波就唔識踢 基本上可以大清洗 見到而家隊巴塞廢到咁真係幾唏噓<br />\n<br />\n不過都要恭喜拜仁 踢得好好 幾腳波就穿巴塞防線 用波好爽<br />\n<br />\n今年歐聯應該唔係拜仁就係曼城<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cbd40c5e73ade88b6190e88a53f43a3a577eb8e","tid":2157071,"uid":218659,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T21:34:58.000Z","msg":"反而覺得得psg威脅到拜仁 尼馬同麥巴比幾勁 雖然中場都麻麻哋"},{"pid":"067cc3c5e02c2a21363c594852af5e353cb71fe1","tid":2157071,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T21:38:09.000Z","msg":"紅牛啦 德超熟晒拜仁條路"},{"pid":"71e55740fecb52e7e6875375762811d0295f17cd","tid":2157071,"uid":35589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9cbd40c5e73ade88b6190e88a53f43a3a577eb8e","tid":2157071,"uid":218659,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T21:34:58.000Z","msg":"反而覺得得psg威脅到拜仁 尼馬同麥巴比幾勁 雖然中場都麻麻哋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T21:39:25.000Z","msg":"入幾多都唔夠後面輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa926e55fae373e4659e25122b094ea93126c2be","tid":2157071,"uid":21255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cbd40c5e73ade88b6190e88a53f43a3a577eb8e","tid":2157071,"uid":218659,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T21:34:58.000Z","msg":"反而覺得得psg威脅到拜仁 尼馬同麥巴比幾勁 雖然中場都麻麻哋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T21:41:25.000Z","msg":"冇form 踢個人能力"},{"pid":"756ed088580be9a7d86329ecad78e3e10fabce7b","